subtitleNullable: Predict eye state with EEG readings.
descriptionNullable: ![](https://www.googleapis.com/download/storage/v1/b/kaggle-user-content/o/inbox%2F10465532%2Fd273d9fd7ec8f3d6d8b212f5a17baefc%2FMicrosoftTeams-image.png?generation=1681544032552252&alt=media)All data is from one continuous EEG measurement with the Emotiv EEG Neuroheadset. The duration of the measurement was 117 seconds. The eye state was detected via a camera during the EEG measurement and added later manually to the file after analyzing the video frames. '1' indicates the eye-closed and '0' the eye-open state. All values are in chronological order with the first measured value at the top of the data.
